test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -2116 == -46
 +  where -2116 = <built-in function prod>([-2, -23, -46])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7217dde079c0>([-46])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7217dde079c0> = [[1, -46], [1, -46, 1], [-46, 1], [-46, 1, -46], [1, -46], [1, -46, 1], ...].count
